{"tid":1166994,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公司電話太多，非常煩。","createTime":"2019-05-22T19:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T08:16:18.000Z","uid":255002,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65d8d945778d691682fc24ed04e581048dbc24f2","tid":1166994,"uid":255002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T19:51:23.000Z","msg":"有冇好似我咁，已經好憎聽到電話響。公司電話真係可以不停響。有<br />\n日試過90個電話。每日平均都20幾30個。煩到呢。專心做嘢時，突然<br />\n響，真係會燥。仲要有時係啲客問白癡問題，真係反眼到後腦。好想<br />\n發明/搵一樣嘢，係電話唔洗響都可以接到電話嘅儀器。<br />\n就係咁，自己手機都係永遠震機。真心好討厭。"},{"pid":"673615fb7fcacf4ce4430a319a0492e33f5412f4","tid":1166994,"uid":227691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"可以揀份唔洗接電話嘅工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfef4cda47731c9e136e23955d0a25d932b72ef","tid":1166994,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"都係你自己聽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668e6b09efb1c60f6a789f7c7c7e5c01956c7ed6","tid":1166994,"uid":239464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}